        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Plastic Pellet Free Waters Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Environmental Protection Agency to issue a final rule that prohibits certain discharges of plastic pellets and other preproduction plastic into waters of the United States.</p>]]></text>
